---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Jennifer Chong | Corporate Governance Consultant Singapore"
  description="Singapore's board governance expert. PhD in Corporate Governance. Specialising in SGX compliance, board effectiveness, and female director recruitment."
>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">🏛 Singapore's Board Governance Specialist</div>
    <h1>Strengthen Your Board.<br><span class="highlight">Achieve Governance Excellence.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Help your board enhance effectiveness, reach compliance targets, and build diverse leadership — backed by research, grounded in Singapore's regulatory reality.</p>

    <div class="hero-value-box">
      <p>Most Singapore boards know governance matters. But do you know where you stand?<br>A comprehensive board assessment reveals:</p>
      <ul class="hero-value-list">
        <li>Where you stand vs. SGX compliance</li>
        <li>Your board's effectiveness gaps</li>
        <li>Specific recommendations for improvement</li>
        <li>Your path to governance excellence</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Free Board Assessment</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Learn About Services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== STATS BAR ===== -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">8+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years Board Research & Consulting</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">PhD</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Corporate Governance (Curtin University)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">3+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Peer-Reviewed Publications</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">SGX</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Compliance Specialist (Rules 710–720)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== PROBLEM ===== -->
<section class="bg-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">The Challenge</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The Board Governance Challenge</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Your board is responsible for oversight, strategy, and accountability. Yet many boards struggle with these critical issues.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-item fade-up">
        <span class="x-icon">✗</span>
        <p><strong>SGX Compliance Uncertainty</strong> — unclear where you stand on Rules 710–720</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item fade-up">
        <span class="x-icon">✗</span>
        <p><strong>Rubber-Stamp Decisions</strong> — board effectiveness unclear, strategic debate minimal</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item fade-up">
        <span class="x-icon">✗</span>
        <p><strong>Missing Female Directors</strong> — SGX target is 25% by 2025, most boards fall short</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item fade-up">
        <span class="x-icon">✗</span>
        <p><strong>No Succession Plan</strong> — what happens when key directors retire?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item fade-up">
        <span class="x-icon">✗</span>
        <p><strong>Risk Management Gaps</strong> — unclear who oversees what, risk reporting inadequate</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-item fade-up">
        <span class="x-icon">✗</span>
        <p><strong>Outdated Board Composition</strong> — skills misaligned with current strategy and challenges</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-cta fade-up">
      <h3>Sound familiar? You're not alone.</h3>
      <p>Most Singapore boards face these challenges. The good news: they're solvable — with the right expertise and a structured approach.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== SOLUTION ===== -->
<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">The Solution</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">We Help Boards Move From<br>Compliance to Excellence</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-intro">
      <div>
        <p style="font-size:1.0625rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">I'm <strong>Jennifer Chong</strong>, a corporate governance expert with a PhD in board effectiveness and 8+ years of research on gender diversity in leadership. I work directly with Singapore's boards to deliver real, measurable governance improvements.</p>
        <p>My work combines academic research rigor with practical consulting experience — bridging the gap between governance theory and business reality. Every recommendation I make is grounded in published evidence, not opinion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-photo">👩‍💼</div>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-steps-grid">
      <div class="solution-step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h4>Assess Your Current State</h4>
        <p>Comprehensive board governance audit revealing compliance gaps, effectiveness issues, and specific opportunities for improvement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h4>Develop Your Strategy</h4>
        <p>Board composition roadmap, female director recruitment plan, and 3-year governance improvement strategy tailored to your organisation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h4>Implement &amp; Support</h4>
        <p>Hands-on implementation support including director recruitment, on-boarding, training, and ongoing advisory for sustained results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="result-box fade-up">
      <span class="result-tag">Result</span>
      <p>A more effective board. Better decisions. Stronger leadership pipeline. Improved governance maturity. SGX compliance achieved and maintained.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== SERVICES OVERVIEW ===== -->
<section class="bg-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Our Services</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Core Governance Services</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">From focused compliance reviews to full governance transformation — tailored to your board's specific needs and goals.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-home-grid">
      <div class="service-home-card fade-up">
        <div class="svc-header">
          <div class="svc-badge">Core Service</div>
          <h3 class="svc-title">Board Governance Audit</h3>
          <p class="svc-meta">$12,000–15,000 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 4–6 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <p style="font-size:0.9375rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Complete assessment of compliance, effectiveness, composition, and risk oversight.</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>SGX compliance review (Rules 710–720)</li>
            <li>Board effectiveness evaluation</li>
            <li>Governance gaps identification</li>
            <li>3-year improvement roadmap</li>
            <li>Board-level presentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-home-card fade-up">
        <div class="svc-header">
          <div class="svc-badge">Core Service</div>
          <h3 class="svc-title">Board Effectiveness Assessment</h3>
          <p class="svc-meta">$10,000–12,000 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 4–5 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <p style="font-size:0.9375rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Evaluate how well your board actually functions beyond compliance.</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Board dynamics assessment</li>
            <li>Strategic contribution evaluation</li>
            <li>Risk oversight review</li>
            <li>Individual director feedback</li>
            <li>Improvement recommendations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-home-card fade-up" style="grid-column: span 2;">
        <div class="svc-header featured">
          <div class="svc-badge">Signature Service</div>
          <h3 class="svc-title">Female Director Recruitment &amp; Board Diversity Strategy</h3>
          <p class="svc-meta">$15,000–35,000 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 6–12 months (ongoing)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <p style="font-size:0.9375rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Our signature service. We don't just advise that you need female directors — we find qualified candidates and integrate them successfully.</p>
          <div class="grid-2" style="gap:1rem;">
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Board diversity audit</li>
              <li>10–15 female director candidates identified</li>
              <li>Recruitment strategy &amp; implementation</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>On-boarding program design</li>
              <li>12-month diversity monitoring</li>
              <li>SGX diversity target achievement plan</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline-navy btn-lg">Explore All Services &amp; Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CREDENTIALS ===== -->
<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Why Choose Me</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Research Rigour. Practical Results.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="credentials-grid">
      <div class="credential-card fade-up">
        <div class="credential-icon">🎓</div>
        <h4>PhD in Corporate Governance</h4>
        <p>Research-backed recommendations grounded in academic rigour, not opinions. Every insight is anchored in published evidence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card fade-up">
        <div class="credential-icon">📄</div>
        <h4>Published Researcher</h4>
        <p>Work published in leading journals: Gender in Management, Journal of General Management, MATEC Web of Conferences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card fade-up">
        <div class="credential-icon">🏢</div>
        <h4>8+ Years Board Expertise</h4>
        <p>Direct consulting and research experience with Singapore's boards across construction, finance, education, and manufacturing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card fade-up">
        <div class="credential-icon">📋</div>
        <h4>SGX Compliance Specialist</h4>
        <p>Deep knowledge of Singapore's specific regulatory environment, SGX Listing Rules, and Code of Corporate Governance requirements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card fade-up">
        <div class="credential-icon">👥</div>
        <h4>Female Director Specialty</h4>
        <p>Unique expertise in board diversity. I don't just say you need women — I identify qualified candidates and integrate them successfully.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card fade-up">
        <div class="credential-icon">🏫</div>
        <h4>Active Academic &amp; Lecturer</h4>
        <p>Current Lecturer at ERC Institute Singapore. Visiting Lecturer at Swansea University, University of Chichester, and Deakin University.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TESTIMONIALS ===== -->
<section class="testimonials-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Client Feedback</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">What Boards Say</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card fade-up">
        <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">Within 6 months, we moved from one female director to three. Jennifer didn't just identify candidates — she prepared us to integrate them successfully.</p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">— Board Chair, Construction Company</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card fade-up">
        <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">The board governance audit revealed gaps we didn't know we had. The recommendations were specific, actionable, and immediately useful.</p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">— CEO, Education Institution</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card fade-up">
        <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">Jennifer's approach is unique: she combines research rigour with practical understanding of how boards actually work in Singapore's business environment.</p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">— Board Member, Finance Sector</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== FINAL CTA ===== -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to Strengthen Your Board?</h2>
    <p>A free 30-minute board assessment call reveals where you stand and what's possible.</p>
    <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Free 30-Minute Assessment Call</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">View All Services</a>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-contact-row">
      <span class="cta-contact-item">📧 jennifercly@gmail.com</span>
      <span class="cta-contact-item">📞 +65 8577 6630</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
